stories.text:
It seems like every service that I sign up for wants an email address to even look at information on their websites. Without much effort, I end up with a bazillion emails from all of these services. It feels like I want to set up aliases to at least group messages by the type of service but that even gets unwieldy at some point. How do y'all manage this?

Thank you for your time.
